Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}破后重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}生命初始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}现在虽然感受不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}心中仍能隐约触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\fs28\be1\blur3}第十八话 凯特的朝与夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍的诸位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 注意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在暑假里最后的盛典——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍主办的烧烤派对就要开始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……话说回来 我就这点儿号召力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家从自己家里过来 还要一段时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是放暑假了还留在宿舍里的家伙 才不正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才来到南方小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是暑假 不留在这里不是很浪费吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 本田学长不是也在宿舍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打工时留下的心理创伤 还没有痊愈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好记住了 一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说只是小小的打工  但是真正出了社会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有意想不到的困难在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是我叫来的 我就猜到人不会太多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的气氛真是转换的恰到好处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 没得到许可 不要自作主张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚本来是打算在寂静中 品味夏日的结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个活动怎么说也是宿舍一代代流传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为住宿生准备的传统活动……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木炭就放在这儿可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 沸腾的夏日还没有结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(300,0)}现在 真心话大冒险烟火大会进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 其实期末考试的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里听到的可疑的响雷 是我肚子的在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}玉屋：旧意为日本烟火商店的铺号，与「键屋」一起在江户两国地区每年初夏举行的烟火大会中博得好评 转指放烟火时观众的好评。现意一般是放烟火时人们的欢呼声。此处为游戏接续的呼号。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 之前我给塔科特君做便当的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没做好的可乐饼中 花了5分钟施加上爱的念力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我经常让女仆帮我搓背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我初吻的对象是我养的小猫李奥纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我不吃青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其实之前散布宿舍长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿泳装做100回单杠翻转的录像就是我玉屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 那个……那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前……不是 不是……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}太过于光明磊落 没有秘密 也不见得是好事呢=V=
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是塔科特君输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把鞋跟袜子都脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再脱我就……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 那边好像很热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脱吧 塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像玩得很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉祥物男孩 这回是跳脱衣舞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟 这位小帅哥也很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们突然就闯进来 还真是厚脸皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(350,0)}这太危险了 玩儿烟花的人千万不要模仿啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君 快阻止她们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 宿舍长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-还给我                          -不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夏天真的「燃」起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「燃」过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万幸的是 没有出现受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是房间的小火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特纳西君的房间被烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要考虑一下你今后的住处才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他来我家借宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢啦 诹访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都烧光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假最后的庆典就是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把换洗的衣服放在这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢……谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够呛啊 你也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话 我来给你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不……不用费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用了……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 事先把这个放到口袋里 真是明智啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的怀表么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服还有教科书的话 总有办法解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的事明天再考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我也不是很消沉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 毕竟是塔科特君嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是诹访君 以前住过的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是诹访小时候画的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候经常来这里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了 给你看个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君的相册
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候经常模仿明星的样子玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮琪·凯特班长？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候经常一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}第二学期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 和子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人 都转到我们班上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安多利光和景圆香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在我们班真是人气越来越旺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是琉璃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲亲~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我给学长做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说这算是给做料理的手一份奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是奖励呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友的暑假一完结
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友的新学期又开始啦~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子 你已经决定好要哪个了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍的火灾 真是灾难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家稍微玩了下烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家财和生活用品全都化为飞灰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实在的真是个危机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要找份兼职什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时住在诹访家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我家里也可以哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩火的话 跟我玩不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个貌似会烧的伤痕累累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 我在诹访家的相册上看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说以前你说过要跟和子组成一个偶像组合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候说过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是和现在的形象完全不一样的相片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是10多年前的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而和子到现在还说想成为歌手什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待朝阳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的小小世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一去不复返的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无动于衷的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋色之风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大人的步伐一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将昔日往事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我娓娓道来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来往往 不时的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那独一无二的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启程寻找 破后重生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是等待的终焉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵引出深埋心中的悲伤的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破后重生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命初始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便现在没有察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实已在心中全部接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住双目 依旧可以洞察一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonder（这真是太奇妙了）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确这世上 总是有很多出人意外的惊喜等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把店里的工作放一边 只顾着玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每天这样吊儿郎当的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你还真想当明星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是今天开始来店里帮忙的的塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果看上他的话 招他入赘也没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉屋……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}此处玉屋应承开头的游戏，有“看到了劲爆消息”之意。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heigent仍然无法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才能让它复原呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就目前来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是计算能够引导出\N你和目前的oreichalkos的波动周期的极值
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要花几天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且复原后的cybody
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要总会的许可才能用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原来以为它能够轻松复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多次疯狂使用都可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为到了第4阶段后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计不必再需要这样复杂的机械接口程序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单凭随Driver的意志 就可以随意复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目前的阶段想要复原 可是有生命危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说如果失败了的话 可能会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真够无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启程之日来临后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真让他们操作着cybody走出零空间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为所欲为的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界真的会变得一团糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是也开始变得无聊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再快一点让我玩玩它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有玩具 我好寂寞~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是有真正印记的Star Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕Cybody坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该可以使用第一阶段的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对噢 那样也挺有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公演就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野也离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还要找新的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其把这个当做柔软体操
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如把它当成是宣传的一环来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们还有人气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们那哥俩好的样子 让我有点讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的那件事……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不会跟别人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是演剧社的粉丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的粉丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:16:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是转到2班的学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安多利光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景圆香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对演剧社可没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是1班的班长妮琪·凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能就是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 但比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前和他们玩才是 第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团排练的日子 不要练了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能击中我一次 就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一脸不满的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 我可以不收你房费
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:22.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:24.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老老实实给我放弃这个天真的念头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位帅哥 用木刀来练本身就够天真了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我要上了 房东
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管来吧 房客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heigent第一阶段 魔镜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,star sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是上次的……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刀法是……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是塔科特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的黑暗是window star的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要身处其中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了自己之外的人都会以window star的姿态现身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始我要袭击你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要注意 千万别自相残杀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pinch（陷入了危机啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就让你结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这黑暗中 你除了自己可分辨不出敌我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能分辨出自己就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说叫你稍微给我手下留情些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}使用第一阶段的人 请勿模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超刺激啊 新藤诹访真是不可轻辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 他只不过是为了保命才这样做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 真是不知道手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种性格 为什么会这么受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是早就说过了么 诹访君其实是很温柔的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 反正他也让我借住了得说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的时候 他看到我模仿明星的样子时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是会很高兴的称赞我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 班长也……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长 现在也对诹访……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于辟西之巫女去做什么工作了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 并非是我让这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辟西大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里暂时不会有什么问题 但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜他又陷入了沉睡中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诹访君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周日是和子的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要亲手做饭为她庆生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们一起上街时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团的魔爪有向我们袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 Star Driver 闪亮的塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.85,0:24:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人的周日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河已经开始闪耀了
